values:
So... today was great alright. People are so dumb.
I think we should all just crawl into an effing hole and stay there for life.

I wish Saskatchewan and Alberta were just colonies in my pocket. Somewhere I could go to get away from this shit life I have right now. I miss everyone.

Why do the people I love the most live so far away?


I work Christmas day for Pete's sake. WHY?!?!

Fuck.

Someone explain why I'm here?


      cut here
Goodness moley! I havent been here in quite some time! just thought id drop in. nothings changed.
Too bad I barely know what I'm doing... dag, yo.
